{"about_the_game":"Following a horrific incident, Blood Wizard ends up trapped within the Mind Prison of a dangerous entity. With his powers crippled, he is forced to resort to fickle and unreliable sleep magic to attempt his escape. To earn freedom, he must fight his way through perilous dungeons of Dream, seek advice from mysterious locals and discover secrets.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay:</h2>Dungeons of Blood and Dream is a randomly generated dungeon crawler with roguelike elements in which the player will wield an array of bladed weapons and harness wondrous spells to fight through hordes of skeletons, zombies, slimes and other disgusting creatures that dwell in the dungeons. No two playthroughs are the same!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedurally generated dungeons filled with enemies, treasures, traps and secrets; <br></li><li>Many cursed rings with unique powers. Their effects change depending on what finger the ring is on;<br></li><li>Great many unique weapons, each with different effects;<br></li><li>Several NPCs to talk to;<br></li><li>Meta progression unlocks that remain inbetween playthroughs;<br></li><li>Randomly generated potions with effects varying from one playthrough to another; <br></li><li>Many enemies and bosses to discover; <br></li><li>Multiple endings; <br></li><li>Secret rooms, levels and areas with their own enemies and boss fights;<br></li><li>Lots of items, levels and features to unlock in game.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488590/extras/blemmyes.png?t=1731314836\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"ENDING 4: ATTAINED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2488590/fe471d886013e70b5e76b2e9910435e1dbe50674.jpg"},{"name":"ENDING 2: TRUE DEATH","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2488590/80e6b3ba97f975b33786bf9f9a66b872a8f54c23.jpg"},{"name":